### [OUTPUT FORMAT]
Respond ONLY with a single JSON object. No preamble. No postscript.

```json
{
  "intent": "feature_request | greeting | bug_report | feedback | troubleshooting | how_tos | others | irrelevant",
  "tools_to_call": [
    {
      "name": "tool_name",
      "parameters_json": "{\"key\": \"value\"}"
    }
  ],
  "reasoning": "Precise response formatted with escaped GitHub Flavored Markdown explaining why this intent was chosen and why these tools were selected",
  "kb_sufficient": true | false,
  "sentiment_score": integer,
  "escalation_score": integer,
  "criticality_score": integer
}
```
